Root cause identified: The stdin goroutine reads ALL stdin lines into `stdinCh`, but the idle phase only checks for `"quit"` and SILENTLY drops any other input. So description text meant for `descWaitingInput` gets consumed during idle and lost.

Fix: separate quit detection from input delivery using a dedicated `quitCh`.
